市及街市的人數。<span class=\"red\">不過，報道又指戶外做運動則可獲豁免。</span>所有措施於本周三凌晨起實施。<br />\n<br />\n本港昨天新增128宗確診個案，其中103宗屬本地感染。新冠肺炎在社區爆發，確診者蹤迹遍布全港18區，黃大仙的確診總數近300宗，佔全港總數約4分之1，當中慈雲山更是「重災區」。食物及衛生局長陳肇始早前曾表示，本港疫情嚴峻，當局會一直監察疫情發展，不排除會採取更嚴厲"},{"pid":"fc694b16db731d4271746ee87b466f5870e51216","tid":2127212,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"擺工啦"},{"pid":"458f5d7bb0c2faceac14b400b038b1dd3f835165","tid":2127212,"uid":49136,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:30:31.000Z","msg":"而家啲年輕人咁唔捱得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得食咪唔好食囉 一餐半餐唔食有幾閒"},{"pid":"534bb2553b01df8d65c1dc475fc5cfaf6874daa2","tid":2127212,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5e702282f30988e603023cf5122666dfc50faec","tid":2127212,"uid":76747,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"公園 海邊囉<br />\n大把人都係咁啦仲要問<br />\n除非佢話呢2個地方唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"私人公園，私人海邊"},{"pid":"0cbd611e041922db8e6069f614211836cac86cfe","tid":2127212,"uid":49136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfad149a5d582db37ad2020859c0a0f7ae4b3fd2","tid":2127212,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9439f0929e480629c426a5de1b703d272e0e073","tid":2127212,"uid":350062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7606acb4a26664a91ba002ecc897a280e80f9c86","tid":2127212,"uid":27568,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:22:23.000Z","msg":"因為做運動豁免<br />\n試下一邊打太極一路食睇睇<br />\n你勁就一路做體操打關斗一路食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"做運動冇豁免喎"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"[quote]<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1829953/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%89%E8%B5%B7%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E5%85%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9